## 🔧 API Setup

Supports any OpenAI-compatible API:
- **DeepSeek** (default): `https://api.deepseek.com/v1`
- **OpenAI**: `https://api.openai.com/v1`
- **Local LLM**: `http://localhost:1234/v1`

